source: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_000<tab>Come, Dawon! We've a spot of game that wants for hunting.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_000<tab>Regarde, mon petit<var 1D /var>! Nos proies sont venues à nous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_050<tab>Dawon was...defeated? So they've bark <var 1A 02 /var>and<var 1A 01 /var> bite, then.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_050<tab>Vous avez vaincu Dawon<var 1D /var>!? Bah ça, c'est la meilleure<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_051<tab>Perhaps I'll take your measure another time. Until we meet again.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_051<tab>Allez, faut savoir quand tirer sa révérence<var 1D /var>! J'espère qu'on aura à nouveau l'occasion de s'amuser ensemble<var 1D /var>!
